data.description: Close to shopping, 41 and 75 this home is right off of Bayshore Rd on a quite oversized lot at the end on a cul-de-sac. This is a corner lot shaded with old growth trees and smaller flowering and fruit trees that also includes a large shed and large parking area for your motorhome. The interior of the home is also expansive with over 2300 sq ft of living area including 3 oversized bedrooms and an addition area that is designed as a safe room currently used as an office. The living room is towards the back and has access to the pool area through a set of French Doors. The pool is large enough to do laps and is all screened and surrounded by plants as well as a full private back yard. Not in a flood zone and and no damage from the storm.
